Author: goddamnroommate
Text: I commit to two shopping trips. I buy the things I’m interested in and then return what I don’t like so I can try things on at home. The key is actually returning the things lol

Author: LolitaJane
Text: mood.  I'm in my 30s and  I can remember all 3 times in the last decade that I've gone clothes shopping, because it's been horrible and distressing every time.  My mom sends me a big bag of clothes a few times a year, and I just wear those.  Thank you mommy for not making me go to the mall.
